text: Allie Grant (born February 14, 1994) is an American actress. In The Suite Life of Zack and Cody, she played Agnes. She also played Lisa in Suburgatory. Grant was born in Tupelo, Mississippi. ==References== Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:Actors from Mississippi Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:People from Tupelo, Mississippi
